Update notes. (Alpha 0.1.0)
	Features:
		Added swords: Stone and Copper.
		Added Copper Bricks.
		Added grid mode, accessed by pressing 'G'.

	Changes:
		Toolbar is now saved.
		Turning enemies off now despawns all current enemies.
		Increased arrow cooldown.

	Fixes:	
		Overlapping notification text.
		Enemy hitboxes adjusted.
		Held object no longer remains the same on load.
		Bow shooting animation.
		Enemies can no longer walk over holes in the ground.
		Loot box no longer attaches to stone.
		Recipes for copper pickaxe and axe are less glitchy.
		Fixed paused music glitch.

	Outside the game:
		Added google authentication.


